<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.6">
<l>kāyama larniṟavā karumukil pōluruvā</l>
<l rend="indent">kāṉaka māmaṭuviṟ kāḷiya ṉucciyilē</l>
<l>tūyana ṭampayilum cuntara veṉciṟuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">tuṅkama takkariyiṉ kompupa ṟittavaṉē</l>
<l>yāyama ṟintuporu vāṉetir vantamallai</l>
<l rend="indent">yantara miṉṟiyaḻit tāṭiya tāḷiṇaiyā</l>
<l>yāyave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vaṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who takes the colour of the Kāya blossom!</l>
<l rend="indent">You who has a complexion like a dark cloud!</l>
<l>O my beautiful child who practices the holy dance</l>
<l rend="indent">on the head of Kāḷiya in the great pond in the forest!</l>
<l>You who plucked out the tusk of the tall, frenzied elephant!</l>
<l>You who has a pair of feet that dance,</l>
<l rend="indent">knowing [how to] wrestle, having destroyed without pause the wrestlers</l>
<l rend="indent">who came in opposition [to you] to do battle!</l>
<l>O Cowherd, dance one time for me!</l>
<l rend="indent">Fighting bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
